In this project we are going to explore Springboot things that we discovered in the tuttorial videos
Following is the sequence in which thhis project has been modified and the topics covered in that

    1. HomePage - Basic Java class that helps to understand RESTApis concept.
    2. ProductServive - GetProductBByID method - used tthe concept of STream API to fetch the product details
                        from the database.
    3. ProductService - Creating method to add products into the list
    4. ProductService - Creating method to update the existing products
    5. ProductService - Deleting the product
    6. Added the JPA and H2 Database dependencies
    7. Added the url and driver inside the application.configurattion file
    8. Created a new package Repository to connect with database
    9. Created a StudentRepo interface which extends JPARepository and now we will use its objects inside
       service layer to communicate with the database.